2. Irrelevant and Intrusive Questions;
3. Dismissal of Diagnosed Physical Condition;
4. Inappropriate Referrals and Lack of Pain Management;
5. Inaccurate and Inappropriate Outcome Letter;
6. Inappropriate Exercise Leaflet Provided.
